                              'Bricky' 1.02

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Bricky' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} in which you have to place bricks
in all the empty spaces of a triangular shaped board. If that sounds
simple, there's one little catch: similar bricks must never touch;
if that happens, those bricks will explode and will be removed from
the board.

  Have fun!

